## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all potential strategies for future-proofing careers. The rapidly changing nature of technology and job markets means that new strategies may emerge that are not covered in this report. Additionally, the perspectives are primarily from Western sources, which may not fully represent global trends and needs.